	  Python wrapper module around the OpenSSL library.

	  https://github.com/pyca/pyopenssl

comment "python-pyopenssl needs a toolchain w/ C++"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_PYTHON3
	depends on !BR2_INSTALL_LIBSTDCPP
